There are several benefits of innovation in business. Firstly, we need to innovate to resolve complex problems. Our companies often face a lot of issues, such as logistics, human resources, quality of products. These problems are too complex to manage easily. Therefore, we need to hold a large meeting, make a plan, and do an innovation. Secondly, innovation helps us increase productivity significantly. By applying technology to our companies, we can make more products in less time. In addition, if we innovate our companies successfully, we will have more advantages compared to competitors. Customer will choose us before our product cheaper and better.
